scenes.description: The VTubers perform an instrumental remix of 'Shiny Smily Story'. Cecilia Immergreen leads on violin, Mori Calliope on bass, Watame on flute, Nerissa Ravencroft on tambourine, Ina'nis on drums, Elizabeth Rose Bloodflame on piano, and Raora on trombone.
The performers celebrate after finishing the song.
A small green creature named Otomo appears and begins to glow and dance, learning the emotion 'joy'.
The VTubers thank the audience and bid farewell as they exit the stage.
Cecilia is alone on stage, reflecting on the performance and introducing the next emotion to teach Otomo: laziness. She presents options for the audience to vote on.
